    "title": "ACC Limited is Hiring: Quality Control Engineer (Mid-Level)",
    "description": "We at ACC Limited are looking for an experienced Quality Control Engineer based out of Agra. If you are a result-oriented professional with a passion for excellence, we want to hear from you.\n\nAbout ACC Limited:\nACC Limited is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Conduct root cause analysis for quality rejections and defects\n• Ensure environmental compliance and waste management\n• Train and supervise shop floor workers and supervisors\n• Monitor equipment performance and coordinate preventive maintenance\n• Manage raw material procurement and inventory levels\n• Implement lean manufacturing and continuous improvement initiatives\n• Oversee daily production operations to meet output targets\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• MBBS / MD / MS from recognized medical college\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Statistical Process Control\n• Proficiency in PPAP\n• Proficiency in Quality Control\n• Proficiency in AutoCAD\n• Proficiency in APQP\n• Proficiency in Root Cause Analysis\n• Proficiency in SolidWorks\n• Proficiency in PLC/SCADA\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Agra, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with ACC Limited!",
